<br>
It's a game.  A diversion.  If you have fun at it, great.  But quit making it out to be some huge be-all-end-all cancer cure seeking journey.  Jesus, get some perspective.<br>
<br>
The game was designed to eat up your time.  Hopefully you have fun while it's doing it, but in the end, its a waste.  No accomplishment in this game will make a difference to the rest of the world.  <br>
<br>
It's not a sour outlook on things, it's the reality of the situation.  If you're having fun, great!  But don't act as if the entire world revolves around whether you play EQ.  I certainly hope that it is a minor part of your life, and not something you do to add validity to your existence.<br>
