<br>
If you wanted - and I did - you could get your own group together and go to Kedge Keep, or mistmoore til level 45-46.<br>
<br>
Kunark changed 2 things. Overcrowding - for pickup groups - and offering &quot;options&quot; at leveling. With loio, frontier mountains, overthere, dreadlands and skyfire you could level up to level 60 in outdoor zones with unlimited amounts of mobs to pull from. If you compare that to the old world, where past level 30 you can't realistically level up except for a few static npcs that were incredibly overcamped back in the days. the mechanics and requirements of outdoor groups vs dungeon groups just aren't as involved, especially at a time where pacify didn't work, and bards couldn't mez.<br>
