The resist rate on pixie strike though, was extremely high, and kept going up as you leveled - as far as I remember, but I never played a bard at these levels. It worked for a few weeks (or months?) but for some reason they upped the resist rate on it at one point. <br>
<br>
I wasn't playing in the first few months of the release, but when I started pacify basically didn't work for all intent and purpose. You'd get aggro on a resist very often, and you couldn't tell wether or not it worked - Most of the time on a &quot;successful&quot; message, nothing actually happened. Most of the time it was a way to get more mobs than you would have had otherwise, and aggro on someone that you didn't want aggro on (the enchanter or the cleric). Bard lull did work to a moderate extent though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4101.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4101.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=4101.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=4101.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4101.topic&index=55><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=4101.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4101.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.unsubscribeUnregiste